%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Xi%20Jinping%20used%20'a%20human%20Chinese%20wall'%20of%20soldiers%20to%20block%20eye%20contact%20between%20him%20and%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20new%20book%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22China%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20sitting%20at%20the%20Great%20Hall%20of%20the%20People%20in%20Beijing%3B%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20attending%20the%20UFC%20313%20event%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20Nevada.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cfee85b8b41a9673fa3cfd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20her%20memoir%20%26quot%3BCareless%20People%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarah%20Wynn-Williams%20wrote%20that%20China's%20leader%2C%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%20was%20surrounded%20by%20a%20%26quot%3Bphalanx%20of%20men%26quot%3B%20during%20the%202016%20APEC%20summit.%3Cp%3EPedro%20Pardo%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3B%20Chris%20Unger%2FZuffa%20LLC%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%20wanted%20to%20talk%20to%20Xi%20Jinping%20at%20the%202016%20APEC%20summit%20in%20Lima%2C%20Peru.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20had%20a%20dressing%20room%20next%20to%20Xi%20and%20back-to-back%20speeches%20with%20the%20Chinese%20leader.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20Xi%20swept%20past%20with%20enough%20people%20to%20create%20a%20%26quot%3Bwall%26quot%3B%20between%20them%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20talk%20never%20happened.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20hoping%20he%20could%20meet%20China's%20leader%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-xi-jinping-meeting-private-sector-big-tech-personal-approval-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EXi%20Jinping%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20APEC%20summit%20held%20in%20Lima%2C%20Peru%20back%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Xi%20didn't%20seem%20interested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-favorite-president-andrew-jackson-new-book-says-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESarah%20Wynn-Williams%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20former%20Facebook%20executive%2C%20said%20she%20was%20with%20Zuckerberg%20when%20the%20botched%20attempt%20at%20a%20meeting%20took%20place.%20She%20detailed%20the%20incident%20in%20her%20memoir%2C%20%26quot%3BCareless%20People%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20was%20published%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20book%2C%20Wynn-Williams%20wrote%20that%20she%20had%20tried%20to%20engineer%20a%20%26quot%3Bspontaneous%20encounter%26quot%3B%20between%20Zuckerberg%20and%20Xi.%20She%20did%20this%20by%20securing%20a%20dressing%20room%20for%20Zuckerberg%20next%20to%20Xi's.%20Per%20her%20account%2C%20she%20also%20arranged%20for%20Zuckerberg's%20keynote%20speech%20at%20the%20summit%20to%20take%20place%20before%20Xi's.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20chance%20encounter%20Wynn-Williams%20and%20Zuckerberg%20were%20hoping%20for%20did%20not%20pan%20out.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Wynn-Williams%20said%20that%20Zuckerberg%20found%20himself%20being%20blocked%20from%20Xi's%20view%20by%20the%20Chinese%20leader's%20hefty%20security%20detail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20phalanx%20of%20men%2C%20in%20identical%20gray%20uniforms%2C%20marching%20in%20formation%20past%20us.%20Mark%20stares%20in%20disbelief%2C%20mouth%20open.%20They%20just%20keep%20coming%2C%20dozens%20and%20dozens%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Wynn-Williams%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20almost%20comical.%20Just%20when%20you%20think%20there%20could%20not%20be%20any%20more%2C%20more%20step%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20men%20ended%20up%20forming%20an%20%26quot%3Bimpenetrable%20dividing%20line%26quot%3B%20between%20Xi's%20and%20Zuckerberg's%20dressing%20rooms%2C%20Wynn-Williams%20wrote%2C%20calling%20them%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20Chinese%20wall.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Xi%20is%20so%20obscured%20that%20he%20doesn't%20even%20have%20to%20risk%20making%20eye%20contact%20with%20Mark%2C%26quot%3B%20Wynn-Williams%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20Xi's%20men%20dispersed%20after%20he%20entered%20his%20dressing%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUh%2C%20I%20guess%20that%20pull-aside%20isn't%20going%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20told%20his%20staff%2C%20per%20Wynn-Williams'%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20Zuckerberg%20has%20managed%20to%20meet%20Xi%20on%20other%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202015%2C%20Zuckerberg%20got%20to%20speak%20to%20Xi%20when%20the%20Chinese%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-leaders-greet-chinese-president-2015-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evisited%20Seattle%20for%20a%20two-day%20visit%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20conversed%20briefly%2C%20and%20Zuckerberg%20later%20posted%20an%20image%20of%20himself%20with%20Xi%20on%20Facebook.%20Zuckerberg%20said%20he%20spoke%20to%20Xi%20entirely%20in%20Chinese%2C%20and%20called%20the%20moment%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3Emeaningful%20personal%20milestone%3C%2Fspan%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20October%202017%2C%20Zuckerberg%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple's%3C%2Fa%3E%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-cook%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETim%20Cook%3C%2Fa%3E%20met%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-cook-and-mark-zuckerberg-meet-with-china-president-xi-jinping-in-beijing-2017-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EXi%20at%20Tsinghua%20University's%20business%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Beijing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWynn-Williams%20%E2%80%94%20an%20international%20lawyer%20and%20former%20New%20Zealand%20diplomat%20%E2%80%94%20joined%20Facebook%20in%202011%20and%20became%20its%20director%20of%20global%20public%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20book%2C%20Wynn-Williams%20gave%20her%20account%20of%20Facebook's%20efforts%20to%20enter%20the%20Chinese%20market.%20Facebook's%20leaders%20considered%20making%20major%20concessions%2C%20including%20letting%20Beijing%20control%20how%20and%20what%20content%20was%20displayed%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20book%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Meta%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20stories%20in%20it%20came%20from%20%26quot%3Ban%20employee%20terminated%20eight%20years%20ago%20for%20poor%20performance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20operate%20our%20services%20in%20China%20today.%20It%20is%20no%20secret%20we%20were%20once%20interested%20in%20doing%20so%20as%20part%20of%20Facebook's%20effort%20to%20connect%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20widely%20reported%20beginning%20a%20decade%20ago.%20We%20ultimately%20opted%20not%20to%20go%20through%20with%20the%20ideas%20we'd%20explored%2C%20which%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20announced%20in%202019%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20response%20to%20Wynn-Williams'%20book%2C%20Facebook%20also%20directed%20BI%20to%20Zuckerberg's%20comments%20on%20China%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20Zuckerberg's%202019%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabout.fb.com%2Fnews%2F2019%2F10%2Fmark-zuckerberg-stands-for-voice-and-free-expression%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espeech%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Georgetown%20University%20%E2%80%94%20he%20objected%20to%20the%20censorship%20of%20protests%20on%20platforms%20like%20Facebook's%20competitor%2C%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20then%20called%20censorship%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20reasons%20we%20don't%20operate%20Facebook%2C%20Instagram%2C%20or%20our%20other%20services%20in%20China.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20our%20services%20in%20China%20because%20I%20believe%20in%20connecting%20the%20whole%20world%2C%20and%20I%20thought%20we%20might%20help%20create%20a%20more%20open%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20worked%20hard%20to%20make%20this%20happen.%20But%20we%20could%20never%20come%20to%20agreement%20on%20what%20it%20would%20take%20for%20us%20to%20operate%20there%2C%20and%20they%20never%20let%20us%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFacebook%20never%20made%20it%20across%20China's%20Great%20Firewall%20%E2%80%94%20and%20as%20of%20today%2C%20Meta's%20core%20products%20remain%20shut%20out%20of%20China's%20insular%20social%20media%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20operate%20an%20ecosystem%20of%20social%20media%20applications%20that%20function%20independently%20of%20their%20Western%20versions.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fchina-tech-baidu-shares-soar-ernie-ai-bot-free-deepseek-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBaidu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-superapp-wechat-best-feature-walkthrough-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWeChat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshanghai-lockdown-china-twitter-weibo-censor-content-food-shortage-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWeibo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frednote-fast-becoming-regular-american-window-into-china-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EXiaohongshu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdouyin-tiktok-40-minute-daily-time-limit-users-under-14-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDouyin%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Chinese%20substitutes%20for%20Google%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20X%2C%20Instagram%2C%20and%20TikTok%20%E2%80%94%20are%20what's%20used%20in%20the%20country%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Meta%20and%20the%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxi-used-wall-of-soldiers-block-eye-contact-zuckerberg-book-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741684277000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cfee85b8b41a9673fa3cfd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxi-used-wall-of-soldiers-block-eye-contact-zuckerberg-book-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Zuckerberg%20was%20hoping%20to%20meet%20Xi%20at%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%202016%20APEC%20summit%20held%20in%20Lima%2C%20Peru.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40businessinsider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxi-used-wall-of-soldiers-block-eye-contact-zuckerberg-book-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tiesto's%20ex-lawyer%20saved%20the%20DJ%20%2428%20million%20in%20taxes%20via%20illegal%20offshore%20shelters.%20Now%2C%20the%20lawyer%20is%20on%20the%20hook%20with%20the%20IRS.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tiesto%20DJ%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F58a450dedd0895f0288b45ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETiesto%2C%20a%20world-renowned%20electronic%20dance%20music%20DJ%2C%3Cp%3EAstrid%20Stawiarz%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETiesto%20saved%20%2428%20million%20over%20six%20years%20through%20illegal%20offshore%20tax%20shelters%2C%20court%20documents%20show.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EProsecutors%20now%20want%20the%20tax%20attorney%20who%20masterminded%20the%20scheme%20to%20personally%20pay%20most%20of%20it%20back.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tax%20attorney%20counters%20that%20Tiesto%20should%20be%20responsible%20for%20his%20own%20back%20taxes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20DJ%20Tiesto%2C%20who%20earns%20millions%20a%20year%20spinning%20electronic%20dance%20music%20at%20venues%20worldwide%2C%20will%20be%20midway%20into%20a%20three-show%20swing%20through%20Vegas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20same%20day%2C%20his%20former%20tax%20attorney%20will%20be%20in%20a%20federal%20courtroom%20in%20White%20Plains%2C%20New%20York%20%E2%80%94%20trying%20to%20not%20get%20stuck%20with%20the%20bill%20for%20the%20Dutch%20DJ's%20back%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20prosecutors%20say%20Frank%20Butselaar%20%E2%80%94%20known%20in%20the%20Dutch%20media%20as%20Holland's%20%26quot%3Btax%20attorney%20to%20the%20stars%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20set%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdj-tiestos-tax-attorney-sentenced-hid-income-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20illegal%20web%20of%20offshore%20shelters%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20saved%20Tiesto%20%2428%20million%20in%20US%20taxes%20over%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20have%20not%20accused%20Tiesto%20of%20wrongdoing%20and%20have%20said%20he%20was%20unaware%20that%20the%20offshore%20structures%20were%20illegal.%20Court%20documents%20show%20the%20IRS%20capped%20Tiesto's%20own%20obligation%20at%20%249%2C467%2C085%2C%20an%20amount%20that%20federal%20prosecutors%20say%20the%20DJ%20has%20paid%20%26quot%3Bvoluntarily.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20though%2C%20prosecutors%20are%20taking%20Butselaar%20back%20to%20court%20to%20ask%20a%20judge%20to%20order%20restitution%20for%20the%20balance%20%E2%80%94%20some%20%2419%20million%20in%20Tiesto's%20unpaid%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20filing%20from%20Monday%2C%20March%203%2C%20prosecutors%20said%20that%20if%20Butselaar%20plays%20nice%20and%20agrees%20to%20pay%20without%20a%20fight%2C%20they'll%20cut%20him%20a%20break%20and%20limit%20their%20request%20for%20restitution%20to%20%2415.5%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EButselaar's%20lawyer%20plans%20to%20counter%20that%20his%20client%20is%20broke%2C%20that%20any%20restitution%20amount%20should%20be%20determined%20via%20an%20exhaustive%20hearing%2C%20and%20that%20back%20taxes%20should%20be%20the%20burden%20of%20the%20taxpayer%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20Tiesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Butselaar%20was%20paid%20an%20hourly%20rate%20to%20help%20his%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%2C%20Kerry%20Lawrence%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIf%20anyone%20is%20held%20liable%20to%20pay%20taxes%20on%20the%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20income%20it%20should%20be%20the%20artists%20who%20earned%20it%2C%20not%20Mr.%20Butselaar.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReps%20for%20Tiesto%20%E2%80%94%20given%20name%20Tijs%20Verwest%20%E2%80%94%20declined%20requests%20for%20an%20on-the-record%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b24d9500-d678-4a97-840a-682b6482a6c7%5C%22%3E%2419%20million%20is%20'a%20lot'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhite-collar%20defense%20lawyers%20and%20tax%20law%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they%20had%20never%20heard%20of%20a%20tax%20attorney%20or%20accountant%20being%20ordered%20to%20pay%20such%20a%20high%20amount%20of%20their%20client's%20back%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20last%20week's%20filing%2C%20Butselaar's%20prosecutors%20offered%20US%20District%20Judge%20Cathy%20Seibel%20three%20examples.%20The%20highest%20restitution%20cited%20was%20%242%20million%2C%20the%20amount%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-ndms%2Fpr%2Ftax-preparer-sentenced-18-months-serve-and-196-million-restitution%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20federal%20judge%20in%20Mississippi%3C%2Fa%3E%20ordered%20a%20tax%20preparer%20to%20pay%20the%20IRS%20in%20late%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20federal%20law%20holds%20tax%20preparers%20liable%20if%20it's%20proven%20that%20they%20knowingly%20hid%20their%20clients'%20income%2C%20said%20John%20Moscow%2C%20a%20longtime%20financial%20crimes%20prosecutor%20for%20the%20Manhattan%20District%20Attorney's%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNineteen%20million%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Moscow%2C%20now%20senior%20counsel%20at%20Lewis%20Baach%20Kaufmann%20Middlemiss%20in%20New%20York.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20seems%20appropriate%20for%20the%20federal%20government%20to%20tell%20a%20tax%20preparer%2C%20'You%20knew%20it%20was%20a%20crime%3B%20pay%20it%20back%20to%20us.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20offshore%20structures%20Butselaar%20created%20for%20Tiesto%20hid%20tens%20of%20millions%20in%20income%20earned%20from%20overseas%20performances%20between%202012%20to%202017%2C%20and%20caused%20a%20total%20IRS%20tax%20loss%20of%20%2428%2C020%2C413%20%E2%80%94%20money%20prosecutors%20say%20the%20DJ%20should%20have%20paid%20after%20qualifying%20as%20a%20US%20tax%20resident%20in%20each%20of%20those%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EButselaar%20has%20also%20admitted%20saving%20fellow%20Dutch%20DJ%20Afrojack%20%24700%2C000%20on%20his%202013%20taxes%20through%20an%20identical%20offshore%20shelter%20scheme.%20As%20with%20Tiesto%2C%20Afrojack%20%E2%80%94%20given%20name%20Nick%20van%20de%20Wall%20%E2%80%94%20has%20not%20been%20implicated%20in%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Afrojack's%20%24700%2C000%20tax%20savings%20are%20added%20in%2C%20and%20Tiesto's%20%249%20million%20payment%20is%20subtracted%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20total%20outstanding%20tax%20loss%20to%20the%20IRS%20from%20Butselaar's%20actions%20is%20%2419%2C250%2C845%2C%26quot%3B%20prosecutors%20wrote%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BButselaar's%20efforts%20to%20escape%20his%20restitution%20obligations%20are%20unpersuasive%2C%20unsupported%20by%20law%2C%20and%20contrary%20to%20the%20plea%20agreement%20that%20both%20he%20and%20his%20lawyers%20signed%2C%26quot%3B%20prosecutors%20wrote%20in%20their%20filing%20to%20the%20judge%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20also%20wrote%20that%20they%20hope%20Seibel%20will%20order%20Butselaar%20to%20pay%20up%20immediately%20before%20they%20leave%20the%20courtroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b48ae586-1e4a-497d-a5a0-1620427234b3%5C%22%3EThe%20IRS%20lost%20at%20least%20%2425%20million%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EButselaar%2C%2065%2C%20is%20in%20a%20Westchester%20County%2C%20New%20York%2C%20jail%2C%20serving%20the%20final%20six%20months%20of%20a%2030-month%20federal%20sentence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20November%20tax-fraud%20plea%2C%20he%20admitted%20that%20the%20offshore%20shelters%20he%20devised%20for%20the%20Dutch%20DJs%20and%20fashion%20models%20on%20his%20client%20list%20had%20cost%20the%20IRS%20at%20least%20%2425%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20described%20the%20scheme%20this%20way%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EButselar%20set%20up%20a%20web%20of%20companies%20to%20segregate%20his%20clients'%20US-generated%20income%20from%20their%20overseas%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20overseas%20companies%2C%20typically%20set%20up%20in%20Cyprus%20and%20Guernsey%2C%20were%20controlled%20by%20trusts%20with%20straw%20beneficiaries%2C%20and%20the%20non-US%20income%20that%20flowed%20into%20them%20would%20not%20be%20reported%20to%20the%20IRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EButselaar's%20clients%20would%20report%20only%20their%20US-generated%20income%20on%20their%20tax%20returns%2C%20even%20though%2C%20as%20US%20resident%20taxpayers%2C%20they%20needed%20to%20report%20all%20of%20their%20income%20worldwide.%20Overseas%20citizens%20qualify%20for%20US%20tax-residency%20status%20%E2%80%94%20and%20must%2C%20therefore%2C%20pay%20US%20taxes%20on%20the%20entirety%20of%20their%20income%20%E2%80%94%20if%20they%20live%20in%20the%20states%20for%20183%20or%20more%20days%20in%20a%20single%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20Butselaar%20hid%20between%20%2470%20million%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-sdny%2Fpr%2Finternational-tax-advisor-arrested-helping-conceal-over-100-million-income-high-net%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20%24100%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20reportable%20overseas%20income%20from%20the%20IRS%2C%20prosecutors%20alleged.%20The%20scheme%20was%20discovered%20in%20March%202018%20by%20Dutch%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELearning%20of%20the%20criminal%20investigation%2C%20Tiesto%20hired%20a%20prominent%20international%20law%20firm%2C%20Kramer%20Levin%20Naftalis%20%26amp%3B%20Frankel%2C%20to%20review%20his%20offshore%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Dutch%20criminal%20investigation%20and%20Kramer%20Levin's%20analysis%2C%20Verwest%20eventually%20fired%20Butselaar%2C%26quot%3B%20prosecutors%20wrote%20in%20February%2C%20using%20Tiesto's%20given%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0511c6a-52f9-44e6-a420-61a1343d65d1%5C%22%3EA%20modest%20home%20in%20Italy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Butselaar's%20lawyer%20plans%20to%20argue%20that%20his%20client%20has%20limited%20financial%20means%20and%20that%20the%20judge%20has%20the%20discretion%20to%20order%20no%20restitution%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Butselaar's%20sole%20asset%20is%20a%20modest%20home%20in%20Italy%20that%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20are%20selling%20to%20repay%20a%20loan%20extended%20by%20a%20friend%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20defense%20of%20this%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20Lawrence%20wrote%20the%20judge%2C%20referring%20to%20his%20client's%20holiday%20villa%20in%20the%20medieval%20town%20of%20Valfabbrica%2C%20near%20Perugia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20a%20November%20plea%20deal%2C%20Butselaar%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20a%20single%20tax%20fraud%20count%2C%20telling%20the%20judge%20he%20filed%20a%20false%202013%20return%20for%20Afrojack.%20Lawrence%20now%20argues%20that%20any%20restitution%20should%20be%20limited%20to%20back%20taxes%20relating%20to%20that%20one%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20say%20Butselaar%20approached%20at%20least%20six%20other%20professionals%2C%20including%20American%20CPAs%20and%20tax%20lawyers%2C%20but%20they%20refused%20to%20participate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20professionals%20instead%20told%20the%20tax%20lawyer%20that%20the%20offshore%20income%20being%20accumulated%20outside%20the%20US%20by%20the%20two%20DJs%20needed%20to%20be%20reported%20to%20the%20IRS%2C%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20have%20not%20sought%20charges%20or%20restitution%20against%20Butselaar's%20unindicted%20co-conspirators%3A%20an%20entertainment%20management%20firm%20and%20two%20employees%20who%20did%20agree%20to%20sign%20years%20of%20fraudulent%20tax%20returns.%20Their%20names%20remain%20redacted%20in%20the%20court%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fembed.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25551054-us-v-butselaar-joint-restitution-filing-20250303pdf%2F%3Fembed%3D1%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600px%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiesto-saved-28m-through-illegal-offshore-accounts-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741684261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cb191369253ccddf9897b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiesto-saved-28m-through-illegal-offshore-accounts-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20Thursday%2C%20Tiesto's%20ex-tax%20attorney%2C%20now%20jailed%20on%20tax%20fraud%2C%20will%20fight%20having%20to%20pay%20as%20much%20as%20%2419M%20in%20the%20Dutch%20DJ's%20back%20taxes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22litaliano%40insider.com%20(Laura%20Italiano)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiesto-saved-28m-through-illegal-offshore-accounts-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uproar%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20over%20Kharg