%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20there%20are%20many%20questions%20employers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eeoc.gov%2Femployers%2Fsmall-business%2F4-what-cant-i-ask-when-hiring%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecannot%20legally%20ask%20%3C%2Fa%3Eduring%20a%20job%20interview%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20they%20don't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20worked%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-do-immediately-when-layoff-rumors-start-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHR%20for%20nearly%2020%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20now%20runs%20HRManifesto%2C%20a%20community%20on%20TikTok%2C%20I've%20seen%20it%20happen.%20I'd%20argue%20that%20anyone%20who%20has%20ever%20been%20through%20an%20interview%20has%20probably%20been%20asked%20an%20illegal%20question%20at%20least%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20this%20happens%2C%20it's%20often%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20interviewer%20training.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20some%20interviewers%20intentionally%20ask%20these%20questions%20to%20get%20the%20hire%20they%20want.%20Either%20way%2C%20these%20questions%20are%20illegal%20and%20have%20no%20place%20in%20a%20job%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20big%20ones%20and%20what%20to%20do%20if%20they%20come%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22076326c3-2b62-4754-9aa3-81bd996c3999%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20What's%20your%20age%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBelieve%20it%20or%20not%2C%20it's%20illegal%20to%20ask%20interviewees%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-an-interviewer-asks-your-age-2014-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20old%20are%20you%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eeoc.gov%2Fage-discrimination%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhat%20year%20were%20you%20born%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20interviewers%20ask%20these%20questions%20because%20they%20think%20you%20look%20young.%20They%20mig