of%20Moscow's%20airports%20to%20ensure%20air%20safety%20after%20the%20attacks.%20Two%20other%20airports%2C%20in%20the%20Yaroslavl%20and%20Nizhny%20Novgorod%20regions%2C%20both%20east%20of%20Moscow%2C%20were%20also%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RIA%20news%20agency%20reported%20that%20a%20train%20station%20in%20the%20Domodedovo%20district%2C%20about%2035km%20south%20of%20Moscow%2C%20was%20also%20damaged%20in%20the%20strike.%20Damage%20to%20railway%20tracks%20from%20drone%20attacks%20was%20also%20reported%20in%20the%20Moscow%20region%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20cancellation%20of%20some%20commuter%20trains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20massive%20attack%2C%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20Reuters%20said%20there%20was%20no%20sign%20of%20panic%20in%20Moscow%2C%20where%20commuters%20went%20to%20work%20as%20normal%20in%20the%20central%20part%20of%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussian%20state-controlled%20international%20news%20television%20network%20RT%20posted%20videos%20showing%20residential%20fires%20started%20by%20drones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20Ukraine%20Talks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20massive%20dawn%20drone%20attack%20unfurled%20just%20as%20a%20team%20of%20Ukrainian%20officials%20prepared%20to%20meet%20a%20US%20team%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20to%20seek%20grounds%20for%20possible%20peace%20talks%20in%20the%20three-year-old%20war%2C%20and%20as%20Russian%20forces%20try%20to%20encircle%20thousands%20of%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20in%20the%20western%20Russian%20region%20of%20Kursk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20talks%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20will%20be%20the%20most%20senior%20since%20a%20disastrous%20White%20House%20meeting%20last%20month%2C%20when%20Trump%20berated%20Ukraine's%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20for%20purported%20ingratitude.%20Since%20Trump's%20dressing%20down%20of%20Zelensky%2C%20Washington%20has%20suspended%20military%20aid%20to%20Ukraine%20as%20well%20as%20intelligence%20sharing%20and%20access%20to%20satellite