20her%20smuggling%20operations%20across%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Ranya%20Rao's%20stepfather%20said%20he%20was%20shocked%20and%20pained%20by%20the%20reports%20about%20her.%20%26quot%3BNo%20words%20can%20truly%20express%20the%20depth%20of%20my%20shock%2C%20pain%2C%20and%20devastation%20by%20the%20recent%20developments.%20This%20is%20an%20extremely%20difficult%20time%20for%20my%20family%20and%20me%2C%20and%20we%20are%20struggling%20to%20process%20it.%20The%20officer%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20any%20violation%20of%20law%20on%20the%20part%20of%20Ranya%2C%20the%20law%20will%20take%20its%20course.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20Ranya%20Rao%20married%20Jatin%20Hukkeri%20in%202024%20and%20did%20not%20visit%20them%20or%20invite%20them%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20DRI%20and%20Karnataka%20Police%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20launched%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20gold%20smuggling%20case%20involving%20the%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20has%20also%20sparked%20a%20political%20blame%20game.%20The%20BJP%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20actor%20approached%20two%20ministers%20in%20the%20Siddaramaiah-led%20Congress%20government%20to%20wriggle%20out%20of%20trouble.%20The%20ruling%20Congress%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20tried%20to%20put%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20dock%20and%20alleged%20that%20under%20the%20Basavaraj%20Bommai-led%20BJP%20government%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20Industrial%20Area%20Development%20Board%20allotted%20land%20to%20Ranya%20Rao%20in%202023%20to%20set%20up%20a%20steel%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741680180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fmkj5624g_ranya-rao-gold-split_625x300_11_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-ranya-raos-friend-tarun-konduraju-who-went-to-dubai-with-her-arrested-in-gold-case-7898102%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20friend%20of%20actor%20Ranya%20Rao%2C%20who%20accompanied%20her%20to%20Dubai%2C%20has%20now%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20gold%20smuggling%20case%20as%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)%20expands%20its%20investigation.%20Tarun%20Konduraju%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20a%20prominent%20business%20family%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Target%20put%20a%20target%20on%20its%20own%20back%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Target%20dog%20looking%20sad.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cf18c6b8b41a9673fa2b63%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Jenny%20Chang-Rodriguez%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20few%20activities%20more%20delightful%20than%20getting%20a%20little%20wine%20drunk%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-shopping-comparison-nyc-vs-midwest-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehitting%20up%20the%20local%20Target%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20go%20treasure%20hunting.%20Sure%2C%20you%20pretend%20you're%20there%20for%20a%20legitimate%20reason%20%E2%80%94%20to%20pick%20up%20toilet%20paper%20or%20trash%20bags.%20But%20whatever%20the%20plan%20was%20going%20in%2C%20you%20wind%20up%20with%20a%20basket%20full%20of%20random%20goodies%3A%20a%20bikini%20for%20a%20vacation%20you're%20not%20taking%20and%20party%20favors%20for%20a%20gathering%20you're%20not%20having.%20A%20yoga%20mat!%20Hot%20Cheetos!%20Five%20packs%20of%20gum!%20At%20Target%2C%20the%20world%20is%20your%20oyster%20in%20terms%20of%20stocking%20up%20on%20stuff%20you%20absolutely%20do%20not%20need.%20Even%20if%20you're%20doing%20Target%20sober%2C%20you%20wind%20up%20drunk%20on%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20lately%2C%20that%20Target%20trip%20has%20been%20a%20little%20less%20joyful%2C%20if%20you're%20even%20going%20at%20all.%20The%20Minneapolis-based%20retailer%20has%20been%20going%20through%20a%20rough%20patch%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-shares-plummet-q3-third-quarter-shares-stock-earnings-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprice-conscious%20consumers%3C%2Fa%3E%20cut%20down%20on%20just-for-funsies%20buys%20that%20fuel%20Target's%20sales.%20And%20in%20terms%20of%20politics%2C%20it%20seems%20like%20Target%20can't%20get%20anything%20right.%20For%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20it's%20found%20itself%20at%20the%20center%20of%20America's%20culture%20wars%2C%20drawing%20the%20ire%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-says-lgbtq-pride-backlash-hurt-sales-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econservatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpastor-target-fast-dei-boycott-betrayal-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprogressives%3C%2Fa%3E%20alike.%20For%20some%20consumers%2C%20popping%20into%20Target%20(or%20refusing%20to)%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20political%20statement%2C%20though%20it's%20not%20clear%20what%20statement%20it%20even%20makes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETarget%20can't%20decide%20what%20it%20stands%20for%2C%20ideologically.%20For%20many%20businesses%2C%20that's%20fine%2C%20but%20in%20Target's%20case%2C%20cultural%20relevancy%20is%20baked%20into%20the%20business%20model%2C%20and%20it%20keeps%20waffling%20on%20how%20it%20wants%20to%20be%20relevant.%20What%20Target%20stands%20for%20economically%20isn't%20working%20right%20now%2C%20either%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20operating%20from%20a%20place%20of%20weakness.%20The%20result%3A%20a%20Target%20that%20can't%20keep%20a%2C%20well%2C%20target%20off%20its%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20how%20things%20have%20been%20going%20for%20Target%20lately%2C%20just%20take%20a%20look%20at%20its%20stock%20price.%20Target%20shares%20are%20down%20by%20more%20than%2030%25%20over%20the%20past%20year%20and%20by%20over%2050%25%20since%20their%202021%20peak.%20While%20its%20most%20recent%20quarterly%20earnings%20were%20generally%20in%20line%20with%20Wall%20Street's%20expectations%2C%20it%20hasn't%20reported%20strong%20financial%20results%20since%20the%20pandemic.%20The%20retailer%20also%20said%20sales%20were%20off%20in%20February%20because%20of%20the%20weather%20and%20%26quot%3Bdeclining%20consumer%20confidence%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20has%20anticipated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-best-buy-ceo-warns-higher-prices-increases-trump-tariffs-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariff-related%20price%20increases%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20days.%20Things%20are%20not%20working%20in%20Target's%20favor%2C%20in%20part%2C%20because%20it%20relies%20on%20discretionary%20spending%20%E2%80%94%20basically%2C%20the%20nonessentials.%20As%20people%20pull%20back%20on%20that%20kind%20of%20spending%20amid%20inflation%20and%20worries%20about%20the%20economy%2C%20that%20hits%20Target%20where%20it%20hurts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20expect%20prices%20to%20rise%2C%20and%20that's%20causing%20people%20to%20spend%20more%20conservatively%2C%20and%20that's%20causing%20them%20to%20think%20twice%20about%20throwing%20this%20or%20that%20other%20thing%20into%20their%20cart%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zak%20Stambor%2C%20a%20senior%20retail%20and%20e-commerce%20analyst%20at%20EMARKETER.%20%26quot%3BTarget's%20business%20relies%20on%20people%20throwing%20this%20or%20that%20into%20their%20cart.%26quot%3B%20(EMARKETER%20is%20owned%20by%20Axel%20Springer%2C%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20Business%20Insider.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETarget%20is%20struggling%20to%20differentiate%20itself%20and%20compete%20against%20Walmart%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Costco%2C%20said%20Michael%20Baker%2C%20a%20managing%20director%20and%20senior%20research%20analyst%20at%20D.A.%20Davidson.%20If%20a%20consumer's%20focus%20is%20product%20selection%20and%20wowing%20customers%20with%20compelling%20offers%2C%20Costco's%20the%20answer%20(or%20at%20least%20as%20good%20as%20Target).%20If%20it's%20convenience%2C%20it's%20Amazon.%20If%20it's%20price%2C%20Walmart%20wins.%20%26quot%3BThat%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20Target%20can't%20find%20their%20niche%2C%26quot%3B%20Baker%20said%2C%20but%20the%20niche%20it%20does%20have%20%E2%80%94%20wants%20and%20not%20needs%20%E2%80%94%20is%20one%20that%20doesn't%20work%20great%20in%20this%20environment.%20%26quot%3BWith%20the%20wind%20at%20their%20back%20and%20people%20spending%20a%20lot%20on%20discretionary%20items%2C%20we%20think%20Target%20can%20compete%20reasonably%20well%2C%20but%20in%20a%20more%20difficult%20environment%2C%20the%20increased%20competition%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20or%20so%2C%20I%20think%2C%20makes%20it%20that%20much%20more%20difficult%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETarget%20is%20also%20struggling%20to%20catch%20up%20in%20some%20booming%20areas%20that%20are%20working%20for%20its%20competitors%2C%20like%20groceries%20and%20e-commerce.%20Both%20efforts%20have%20been%20undertaken%20%26quot%3Bhalfheartedly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zhihan%20Ma%2C%20a%20senior%20research%20analyst%20at%20Bernstein.%20Target%20largely%20relies%20on%20its%20stores%20to%20fulfill%20online%20orders%2C%20which%20may%20be%20cheaper%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20up-front%20cost%20to%20implement%2C%20but%20it's%20very%20labor%20intensive%2C%20as%20associates%20are%20expected%20to%20deal%20with%20in-person%20shoppers%20and%20e-commerce%20customers%20in%20tandem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20slow-walked%20investments%2C%20one%20of%20the%20key%20differentiators%20for%20Target%20%E2%80%94%20a%20relatively%20enjoyable%20shopping%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20undercut%20in%20recent%20years.%20Target's%20attempts%20to%20fight%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiddle-class-shoplifting-retail-theft-crime-stealing-stores-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretail%20theft%3C%2Fa%3E%20mean%20more%20merchandise%20winds%20up%20locked%20up.%20Like%20with%20other%20retailers%2C%20some%20locations%20have%20problems%20with%20inventory%20shortages%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstore-aisles-crowded-boxes-dollar-store-pharmacy-retail-apocalypse-shopping-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrowded%20aisles%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20result%20is%20a%20shopping%20experience%20that%20isn't%20a%20bang-up%20time%2C%20which%20is%20especially%20damaging%20for%20Target%2C%20where%20a%20bit%20of%20fun%20is%20part%20of%20the%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20business%20is%20what%20the%20business%20is%20to%20a%20large%20extent%2C%26quot%3B%20Stambor%20said.%20%26quot%3BTarget%20is%20a%20place%20to%20find%20that%20cool%20other%20thing%20that%20you%20didn't%20expect%20to%20throw%20into%20your%20cart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Target%20has%20been%20having%20a%20tough%20time%20financially%20over%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20it%20may%20be%20even%20worse%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20news.%20Yes%2C%20there%20are%20some%20positive%20headlines%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-shoppers-waited-hours-for-wicked-stanley-cups-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStanley's%20%26quot%3BWicked%26quot%3B-themed%20cups%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20everything%20it's%20doing%20with%20Taylor%20Swift.%20But%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20more%20negative%20headlines%20Target%20would%20rather%20not%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20ways%20Target%20has%20sought%20to%20differentiate%20itself%20from%20competitors%20is%20by%20embracing%20a%20rather%20cosmopolitan%20identity.%20It%20does%20collaborations%20and%20deals%20with%20designers%2C%20big-name%20brands%2C%20and%20celebrities.%20It%20tries%20to%20get%20higher-end%20consumers%20in%20the%20door.%20It's%20a%20bit%20fancy%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20a%20reason%20people%20use%20a%20little%20French%20accent%20to%20call%20it%20%26quot%3BTar-jay.%26quot%3B%20That%20means%20some%20of%20its%20consumers%2C%20particularly%20those%20who%20are%20more%20progressive%20leaning%2C%20expect%20more%20from%20it%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20Target%20has%20been%20happy%20to%20oblige.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20some%20ways%2C%20they're%20victims%20of%20their%20own%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20Baker%20said.%20%26quot%3BTarget%20has%20come%20to%20stand%20for%20fashion%20and%20fun%20and%20it%20is%20really%20a%20very%20culturally%20relevant%20retailer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20which%20puts%20it%20more%20in%20the%20crosshairs%20than%20Walmart%20and%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20recently%20as%202020%2C%20Target%20was%20leaning%20into%20this%20identity.%20The%20Minneapolis-based%20retailer%20had%20positioned%20itself%20as%20a%20leader%20on%20racial%20justice%20in%20response%20to%20George%20Floyd's%20murder%20by%20a%20Minneapolis%20police%20officer%20in%202020.%20The%20moves%20seemed%20to%20go%20over%20well%20until%202023%2C%20when%20it%20stumbled%20into%20a%20series%20of%20culture-war%20woes.%20That%20year%2C%20many%20businesses%20faced%20a%20backlash%20after%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbud-light-transgender-controversy-backlash-boycotts-history%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBud%20Light%20marketing%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%20featuring%20the%20transgender%20influencer%20Dylan%20Mulvaney%20sparked%20outrage%20among%20some%20consumers%20in%20the%20spring.%20Heading%20into%20the%20summer%2C%20Target's%20Pride%20month%20collection%20%E2%80%94%20something%20it's%20been%20doing%20for%20years%20%E2%80%94%20became%20the%20subject%20of%20right-ring%20focus.%20Some%20of%20the%20hullabaloo%20was%20completely%20made%20up%2C%20such%20as%20false%20social%20media%20reports%20that%20Target%20was%20selling%20%26quot%3Btuck-friendly%26quot%3B%20bathing%20suits%20for%20children.%20But%20the%20dust-up%20also%20moved%20from%20social%20media%20to%20the%20real%20world%3A%20Some%20angry%20shoppers%20were%20actually%20attacking%20associates%20and%20destroying%20store%20displays.%20Target%20scaled%20back%20its%20Pride%20collection%2C%20moving%20items%20to%20the%20back%20of%20the%20store%20in%20some%20locations%20and%20pulling%20some%20items%20altogether.%20It%20later%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-says-lgbtq-pride-backlash-hurt-sales-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20backlash%20hurt%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Target's%20been%20stuck%20in%20a%20loop%20of%20corporate%20identity%20indecision%20that%20it%20seems%20unable%20to%20get%20out%20of.%20The%20decision%20to%20scale%20back%20on%20Pride%20made%20no%20one%20happy%20%E2%80%94%20some%20consumers%20were%20already%20upset%20about%20the%20merchandise's%20existence%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20and%20others%20were%20upset%20because%20Target%20backed%20down.%20Target%20declined%20to%20comment%20for%20this%20story%2C%20but%20with%20regard%20to%20its%20diversity%20strategy%20and%20business%20outlook%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20pointed%20to%20links%20to%20its%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.target.com%2Fpress%2Ffact-sheet%2F2025%2F01%2Fbelonging-bullseye-strategy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBelonging%20at%20the%20Bullseye%20Strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.target.com%2Fpress%2Frelease%2F2025%2F03%2Ftarget-corporation-reports-fourth-quarter-and-full-year-2024-earnings%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efourth-quarter%20results%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETarget%20has%20taken%20a%20similar%20please-no-one%20approach%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fdiversity-and-inclusion%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%3C%2Fa%3E%20policies.%20In%20January%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-ends-dei-initiatives-memo-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaxing%20multiple%20DEI%20initiatives%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20ending%20its%20three-year%20DEI%20goals%2C%20wrapping%20up%20a%20program%20to%20invest%20in%20Black-owned%20businesses%2C%20and%20stopping%20participation%20in%20external%20diversity-focused%20surveys.%20Target's%20DEI%20efforts%20and%20reversals%20have%20been%20met%20by%20resistance%20on%20several%20fronts.%20On%20the%20right%2C%20the%20retailer%20has%20been%20hit%20by%20a%20lawsuit%20brought%20by%20the%20state%20of%20Florida%2C%20among%20others%2C%20saying%20investors%20weren't%20made%20aware%20of%20the%20risks%20of%20Target's%20DEI%20initiatives%20and%20potential%20backlash.%20On%20the%20left%2C%20the%20Atlanta%20pastor%20Jamal%20Bryant%20has%20called%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpastor-target-fast-dei-boycott-betrayal-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E40-day%20boycott%20of%20Target%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20its%20DEI%20rollback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20time%20a%20company%20is%20visible%2C%20it's%20a%20target%20for%20activists%20who%20have%20one%20agenda%20or%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Brayden%20King%2C%20a%20management%20professor%20at%20Northwestern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20moment%20when%20much%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-dei-tariffs-taxes-business-uncertainty-scaredy-cat-capitalism-anxiety-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecorporate%20America%20is%20anxious%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20political%20environment%2C%20Target%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20bearing%20the%20brunt%20of%20all%20these%20swirling%20emotions.%20Many%20people%20feel%20powerless%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20actual%20politics%2C%20so%20pouring%20their%20frustrations%20into%20things%20they%20can%20control%20%E2%80%94%20where%20and%20how%20they%20shop%20%E2%80%94%20turns%20into%20an%20outlet%20for%20some%20sort%20of%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20issue%2C%20however%2C%20isn't%20that%20Target%20sold%20Pride%20merchandise%20or%20undertook%20DEI%20initiatives%2C%20it's%20that%20it%20so%20openly%20waffled%20on%20all%20of%20it.%20Again%2C%20it's%20similar%20to%20Bud%20Light%3A%20The%20near-ubiquitous%20beer%20brand%20did%20a%20tiny%20marketing%20campaign%20with%20a%20transgender%20influencer%2C%20and%20when%20that%20caught%20fire%20online%20among%20right-wing%20personalities%2C%20the%20company%20panicked%20and%20backed%20down%20instead%20of%20keeping%20calm%20and%20staying%20the%20course.%20When%20a%20company%20capitulates%20to%20backlash%20and%20cowers%2C%20it%20suggests%20what%20it%20initially%20did%20was%20incorrect%20%E2%80%94%20and%20ultimately%20pleases%20nobody.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWavering%20draws%20more%20attention%20to%20the%20issue.%20It%20signifies%20weakness%20%E2%80%94%20which%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Target's%20business%2C%20is%20part%20of%20the%20problem.%20It%20also%20degrades%20trust%20with%20consumers%20and%20turns%20the%20company%20into%20a%20more%20obvious%20target%20for%20activists%20down%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20kind%20of%20seesawing%20back%20and%20forth%20and%20saying%20one%20thing%20and%20doing%20another%2C%20that's%20what%20gets%20brands%20like%20Target%20in%20trouble%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20David%20Albert%2C%20the%20chief%20insights%20officer%20at%20Collage%20Group%2C%20a%20consumer%20research%20firm%20that%20focuses%20on%20multicultural%20audiences.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20seen%20here%2C%20especially%20with%20Target%2C%20is%20that%20they've%20eroded%20that%20trust%20because%20they're%20not%20doing%20what%20they%20say%20and%20they%20don't%20say%20what%20they%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20clear%20how%20much%20the%20political%20noise%20will%20impact%20Target's%20bottom%20line.%20The%202023%20Pride%20backlash%20did%20ding%20sales%2C%20but%20that%20was%20a%20temporary%20problem.%20As%20a%20general%20rule%2C%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20boycotts%20don't%20work.%20Consumers%20are%20set%20in%20their%20ways%20and%20often%20prioritize%20convenience.%20If%20there's%20a%20Target%20down%20the%20street%20or%20a%20Walmart%2030%20minutes%20away%2C%20most%20people%20will%20stick%20with%20Target.%20Also%2C%20if%20you%20really%20start%20to%20worry%20about%20whether%20each%20and%20every%20business%20you%20interact%20with%20aligns%20exactly%20with%20your%20values%2C%20you%20will%20likely%20find%20there%20is%20nowhere%20on%20Earth%20you%20can%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoycotts%2C%20of%20course%2C%20are%20very%20effective%20tactics%20for%20drawing%20attention%20to%20a%20cause%2C%26quot%3B%20King%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20have%20this%20effect%20of%20making%20Target%20look%20bad.%20But%20do%20I%20think%20that%20it%20will%20affect%20what%20Target%20does%3F%20Probably%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20because%20boycotts%20rarely%20work%20doesn't%20mean%20they%20never%20work.%20Bud%20Light%2C%20for%20one%2C%20really%20did%20see%20a%20decline%20in%20sales.%20The%20evidence%20is%20mixed%20on%20whether%20February's%20single-day%20%26quot%3Beconomic%20blackout%26quot%3B%20was%20effective%2C%20but%20there%20are%20at%20least%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.earnestanalytics.com%2Finsights%2Ffebruary-2025-us-consumer-spending-economic-blackout-and-slowing-activity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20signs%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20may%20have%20moved%20the%20needle.%20Ma%2C%20from%20Bernstein%2C%20said%20it's%20too%20early%20to%20tell%20if%20the%20DEI-related%20backlash%20will%20hurt%20Target's%20long-term%20financials%2C%20but%20she%20acknowledged%20that%20it%20may%20introduce%20more%20%26quot%3Bvolatility%26quot%3B%20into%20its%20shorter-term%20results%20if%20it%20continues%20to%20find%20itself%20embroiled%20in%20cultural%20backlashes.%20%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20help%2C%20for%20sure%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20the%20business%20basics%2C%20Target%20has%20plans%20to%20get%20back%20some%20of%20that%20Tarjay%20sheen.%20It's%20amping%20up%20its%20private-label%20offering%2C%20creating%20more%20in-house%20brands%20that%20resonate%20with%20consumers%20and%20give%20them%20a%20reason%20to%20go%20to%20Target%2C%20specifically%2C%20rather%20than%20somewhere%20else.%20It's%20seeking%20out%20more%20flashy%20collaborations%20and%20partnerships%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftarget-looks-to-build-momentum-in-product-categories-with-growth-potential-1034439875%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elike%20with%20Warby%20Parker%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20scaling%20Target%20Plus%2C%20its%20third-party%20marketplace.%20It's%20still%20hoping%20consumers%20will%20do%20a%20spin%20around%20the%20store%20for%20those%20glorious%20little%20splurge%20buys%20on%20top%20of%20the%20basics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20in%20the%20retail%20landscape%2C%20Target%20isn't%20in%20a%20highly%20enviable%20position.%20Between%20price-sensitive%20consumers%20and%20tariff%20whiplash%2C%20the%20macroeconomic%20landscape%20is%20not%20stacked%20in%20its%20favor.%20And%20its%20soft%20business%20outlook%20means%20that%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20culture%20war%2C%20it's%20operating%20from%20a%20place%20of%20weakness%2C%20which%20raises%20the%20chances%20of%20making%20a%20misstep.%20Instead%20of%20companies%20worrying%20they're%20going%20to%20be%20the%20next%20Bud%20Light%2C%20they're%20likely%20starting%20to%20worry%20they'll%20be%20the%20next%20Target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus