0Akram%20admitted%20being%20stunned%20on%20failing%20to%20spot%20a%20single%20PCB%20official%20at%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20presentation%20ceremony.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fwe-were-the-hosts-wasim-akram-stunned-by-iccs-champions-trophy-ceremony-act-7889945%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Black%20Sea%20resort%20town%20is%20suing%20Russian%20ship%20companies%20after%2010%2C000%20people%20had%20to%20shovel%20spilled%20oil%20off%20its%20beaches%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Volunteers%20work%20to%20clear%20spilled%20oil%20on%20the%20coastline%20of%20Anapa%20on%20the%20Black%20Sea.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cfdf42585f1dff88b1ba7f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223379%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELocal%20authorities%20said%2010%2C000%20people%20helped%20clean%20up%20the%20beaches%20of%20Anapa%20after%20a%20severe%20oil%20spill%20in%20the%20Black%20Sea.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FSergey%20Pivovarov%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Russian%20sea%20resort%20town%20of%20Anapa%20is%20suing%20to%20cover%20its%20cleanup%20bill%20from%20a%20huge%20oil%20spill.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20seeking%20211%20million%20rubles%20from%20the%20owner%20and%20operator%20of%20two%20tankers%20that%20breached%20last%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20resulting%20massive%20spill%20has%20underscored%20concerns%20about%20aging%20ships%20carrying%20oil%20and%20gas%20for%20Russia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20summer%20resort%20town%20of%20Anapa%20is%20suing%20two%20shipping%20companies%20for%20%242.4%20million%20after%20an%20oil%20spill%20devastated%20its%20local%20beaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20office%20of%20the%20town's%20mayor%2C%20Vasiliy%20Shvets%2C%20announced%20on%20Monday%20that%20it%20was%20seeking%20211%20million%20rubles%20from%20Volgatransneft%20and%20Kama%20Shipping%2C%20citing%20clean-up%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20firms%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-massive-oil-spill-dark-shadow-fleet-dangers-sanctions-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eowned%20and%20operated%20two%20tankers%20that%20breached%20near%20Anapa%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20a%20heavy%20storm%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EState%20media%20reported%20that%20the%20Volgoneft%20212%20and%20Volgoneft%20239%20carried%209%2C000%20metric%20tons%20of%20low-grade%20fuel%2C%20more%20than%20half%20of%20which%20emptied%20into%20the%20Kerch%20Strait.%20The%20Black%20Sea%20area%20sits%20between%20Russia%20and%20the%20occupied%20Crimean%20peninsula.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnapa%2C%20a%20popular%20holiday%20town%20of%20some%2080%2C000%20people%2C%20was%20hard%20hit%20by%20the%20spill%2C%20which%20contaminated%20over%2030%20miles%20of%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20said%20the%20cleanup%20involved%2010%2C000%20people%20shoveling%20and%20scooping%20blackened%20sand%20and%20polluted%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225942%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20volunteer%20is%20seen%20bundling%20polluted%20sand%20in%20Anapa.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cfdffbb8b41a9673fa3cbc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223845%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnapa%2C%20a%20popular%20holiday%20town%20in%20the%20Black%20Sea%2C%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20increase%20its%20claims%20against%20the%20shipping%20companies%20soon.%3Cp%3ESergey%20Pivovarov%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMoscow%20declared%20a%20federal%20state%20of%20emergency%20in%20mid-January%2C%20as%20the%20oil%20continued%20to%20spread%20nearly%20a%20month%20after%20the%20tankers%20were%20breached.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e825acbd-0a69-4abb-aed6-1fd89a97d867%5C%22%3EOil%20spill%20feeds%20fears%20of%20Russia's%20dark%20fleet%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spill%20drew%20international%20attention%20amid%20concerns%20that%20Russia's%20sanctioned%20energy%20industry%20is%20using%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwestern-sanctions-hit-russia-shadow-fleet-oil-exports-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bshadow%20fleet%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20commercial%20ships%20to%20ferry%20oil%20and%20gas%20to%20foreign%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20such%20vessels%20are%20aging%20tankers%20pulled%20back%20into%20service%20that%20often%20prove%20difficult%20to%20track%2C%20prompting%20fears%20of%20further%20spillage%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20mechanisms%20to%20contain%20the%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Volgoneft%20212%20%E2%80%94%20which%20split%20into%20two%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20Volgoneft%20239%20were%20both%20over%2050%20years%20old.%20Most%20major%20Western%20oil%20companies%20typically%20use%20tankers%20that%20have%20seen%2015%20years%20of%20service%20or%20fewer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20grey-area%20status%20of%20Russia's%20dark%20vessels%20also%20underscores%20concern%20that%20they%20might%20not%20be%20properly%20insured%20to%20cover%20oil%20spills%2C%20leaving%20communities%20hit%20by%20such%20disasters%20to%20shoulder%20cleaning%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Anapa%2C%20a%20popular%20holiday%20town%20of%20some%2080%2C000%20people%2C%20the%20%242.4%20million%20is%20an%20incomplete%20tally%20of%20the%20money%20%26quot%3Balready%20paid%20under%20contracts%26quot%3B%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20December%20spill%2C%20the%20mayor's%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20amount%20is%20not%20final%2C%20and%20in%20the%20future%2C%20the%20administration%20intends%20to%20increase%20the%20claims%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20Russia's%20federal%20statistics%20agency%2C%20the%20average%20monthly%20salary%20in%20the%20Russian%20economy%20was%2087%2C952%20rubles%2C%20or%20about%20%241%2C000%2C%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EM