t%3Btruly%20heavenly.%26quot%3B%20Vanuatu%20Prime%20Minister%20Jotham%20Napat%20ordered%20the%20cancellation%20of%20Mr%20Modi's%20passport%2C%20citing%20concerns%20that%20the%20fugitive%20was%20using%20it%20to%20evade%20extradition%20to%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVanuatu%20%5Bis%5D%20a%20beautiful%20country.%20You%20must%20put%20%5Bit%5D%20on%20your%20bucket%20list.%20Away%20from%20all%20the%20pollution%20and%20noise.%20Truly%20heavenly%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Modi%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20IPL%20chairman%2C%20who%20left%20India%20in%202010%20while%20facing%20allegations%20of%20financial%20fraud%2C%20had%20been%20residing%20in%20London%20and%20was%20known%20to%20have%20acquired%20Vanuatu%20citizenship%20through%20its%20%26quot%3BCitizenship%20by%20Investment%26quot%3B%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Napat%2C%20in%20an%20official%20statement%2C%20instructed%20the%20Citizenship%20Commission%20to%20cancel%20Mr%20Modi's%20passport%2C%20stating%20that%20acquiring%20Vanuatu%20citizenship%20was%20a%20privilege%2C%20not%20a%20right.%20The%20statement%20also%20clarified%20that%20Mr%20Modi's%20passport%20had%20been%20issued%20following%20standard%20background%20checks%2C%20including%20Interpol%20screenings%2C%20which%20revealed%20no%20criminal%20convictions%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20PM%20Napat%20acknowledged%20that%20Interpol%20had%20twice%20rejected%20requests%20from%20Indian%20authorities%20to%20issue%20a%20notice%20against%20Mr%20Modi%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20substantive%20judicial%20evidence.%20Any%20such%20alert%20would%20have%20triggered%20an%20automatic%20rejection%20of%20Mr%20Modi's%20citizenship%20application%2C%20the%20prime%20minister's%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20reportedly%20asked%20Vanuatu%20to%20cancel%20Mr%20Modi's%20passport.%20While%20India%20does%20not%20have%20a%20diplomatic%20mission%20in%20Vanuatu%2C%20its%20high%20commission%20in%20New%20Zealand%20manages%20relations%20with%20the%20island%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Modi%2C%20the%20founding%20chairman%20of%20the%20IPL%2C%20has%20been%20wanted%20by%20India%20on%20charges%20of%20financial%20misconduct.%20He%20is%20accused%20of%20embezzling%20large%20sums%20of%20money%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20IPL%20commissioner%2C%20including%20allegations%20of%20bid-rigging%2C%20money%20laundering%2C%20and%20violations%20of%20the%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Management%20Act%20(FEMA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20multiple%20efforts%20to%20secure%20his%20return%20to%20India%2C%20Mr%20Modi%20has%20remained%20in%20London%20since%202010.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741672740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F0pmrsfl_lalit-modi-_625x300_11_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flalit-modis-truly-heavenly-post-for-vanuatu-after-passport-cancelled-7897271%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20after%20Vanuatu%20cancelled%20his%20passport%2C%20Lalit%20Modi%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%2C%20described%20the%20island%20nation%20as%20%26quot%3Btruly%20heavenly.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flalit-modis-truly-heavenly-post-for-vanuatu-after-passport-cancelled-7897271%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Philippines%20ex-leader%20Duterte%20arrested%20on%20ICC%20warrant%20over%20drug%20killings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741672671000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0f2c%2Flive%2F60f697b0-1203-11ef-82e8-cd354766a224.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp9ykn85401o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rodrigo%20Duterte%20is%20accused%20of%20'crimes%20against%20humanity'%20in%20a%20crackdown%20that%20left%20thousands%20dead.%