ince%20September%202020%2C%20closing%20more%20than%2050%20per%20cent%20below%20their%20record%20closing%20high%20of%20%24479%20on%20December%2017%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bloodbath%20in%20Wall%20Street%20came%20amid%20concerns%20over%20declining%20electric%20vehicle%20sales%20and%20politically%20driven%20protests%20against%20Mr%20Musk%20over%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20Trump%20administration.%20The%20Tesla%20chief%2C%20however%2C%20seemed%20to%20dismiss%20the%20market%20concerns.%20Replying%20to%20a%20post%20on%20X%20about%20the%20largest%20single-day%20drops%20in%20Tesla%20shares%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20fine%20long-term.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Look%20At%20Tesla%20Shares%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20shares%20plunged%2015.4%20per%20cent%20by%20the%20end%20of%20Monday's%20trading%20session.%20It%20was%20the%20largest%20single-day%20percentage%20decline%20since%20September%202020%2C%20when%20shares%20saw%20a%20decline%20of%20over%2021%20per%20cent%20in%20a%20single%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%2C%20Tesla%20stocks%20witnessed%20a%20total%20decline%20of%2041.4%20per%20cent%20year-to-date%20so%20far%20in%202025.%20This%20includes%20a%20drop%20of%20over%2036.6%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20past%20months.%20As%20of%20March%2010%2C%20Tesla%20stock%20has%20fallen%20by%20more%20than%20half%20to%20a%20new%20market%20cap%20of%20%24696%20billion%20after%20reaching%20its%20all-time%20largest%20market%20capitalization%20of%20%241.5%20trillion%20on%20December%2017.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUBS%20has%20also%20lowered%20its%20price%20target%20on%20the%20stock%20to%20%24225%20from%20%24259%2C%20citing%20lower%20delivery%20forecasts%20for%20the%20first%20quarter%20it%20sees%20resulting%20from%20softer%20demand%20for%20Tesla's%20Model%203%20and%20Model%20Y%20vehicles.%20This%20contributed%20to%20the%20sell-off%2C%20along%20with%20broader%20concerns%20about%20the%20US%20economy%20facing%20a%20recession%20and%20a%20widening%20trade%20war%20amid%20President%20Trump's%20tariff%20threats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20ended%20the%20trading%20day%202.7%20per%20cent%20lower--its%20lowest%20closing%20level%20since%20September%20and%20its%20biggest%20daily%20percentage%20decline%20since%20December.%20The%20Dow%20Jones%20Industrial%20Average%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20dropped%202%20per%20cent%2C%20for%20its%20lowest%20close%20since%20November%204%2C%20the%20day%20before%20Mr%20Trump's%20election%20as%20President.%20The%20Nasdaq%20Composite%20plunged%204%20per%20cent%20to%20a%20near%20six-month%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtests%20Against%20Tesla%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%2C%20where%20Mr%20Musk%20is%20chief%20executive%2C%20has%20been%20facing%20protests%20and%20even%20vandalism%20at%20some%20of%20its%20dealerships.%20Last%20week%2C%20shots%20were%20fired%20at%20a%20Tesla%20dealership%20in%20Oregon%2C%20while%20in%20Boston%2C%20someone%20set%20fire%20to%20the%20company's%20charging%20stations.%20Authorities%20also%20arrested%20some%20violent%20protesters%20for%20rallying%20at%20a%20Tesla%20dealership%20in%20Lower%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20a%20recent%20report%20found%20that%20Tesla%20car%20sales%20in%20Germany%2C%20Europe's%20largest%20market%20for%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20fell%20by%2076%20percent%20in%20February%20compared%20with%20a%20year%20earlier%2C%20sounding%20alarm%20bells%20for%20the%20entire%20European%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuestions%20Over%20Musk's%20Leadership%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fall%20in%20Tesla%20stock%20came%20as%20its%20chief%20Musk%20is%20facing%20questions%20about%20how%20much%20attention%20he%20is%20paying%20to%20his%20businesses%20while%20serving%20as%20an%20adviser%20to%20President%20Trump.%20Over%20the%20week%2C%20Mr%20Musk's%20business%20empire%20-%20including%20Tesla%2C%20social%20media%20site%20X%20an