t%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20a%20high%20level%20these%20comments%20are%20consistent%20with%20our%20thematic%20framework%20where%20a%20small%20number%20of%20leading%20companies%20(or%20individuals)%20are%20focused%20on%20training%2Fbuilding%20the%20leading%20LLM%E2%80%A6which%20will%20require%20significant%20compute%2C%26quot%3B%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20analysts%20wrote%2C%20referring%20to%20large%20language%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20been%20some%20hand-wringing%20lately%20about%20how%20strong%20GPU%20demand%20may%20be%20in%20the%20future%2C%20so%20OpenAI's%20comments%20are%20notable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e76e8215-c8ec-4870-8245-22dee95704f5%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20isn't%20worried%20about%20training%20data%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20OpenAI%20isn't%20worried%20about%20the%20supply%20of%20data%20to%20train%20its%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20highlighted%20its%20ability%20to%20use%20its%20GPUs%20and%20existing%20AI%20models%20to%20create%20more%20data.%20This%20is%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-peak-data-google-deepmind-researchers-solution-test-time-compute-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esynthetic%20data%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20it's%20becoming%20increasingly%20useful%20for%20certain%20stages%20of%20the%20model-creation%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BData%20is%20not%20a%20constraint%20in%20the%20way%20that%20compute%20is%20a%20constraint%20(or%20even%20the%20way%20energy%20may%20one%20day%20be)%2C%26quot%3B%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20AI%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Eabarr%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%