%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fvaranasi-malnutrition-1741180184.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fvaranasi-malnutrition-1741180184-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fvaranasi-malnutrition-1741180184-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fvaranasi-malnutrition-1741180184-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fvaranasi-malnutrition-1741180184-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-411781%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20district%20administration%20launched%20numerous%20initiatives%20that%20helped%20reduce%20malnutrition%20in%20Varanasi.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20years%20earlier%2C%20the%20crisis%20was%20clear%3A%20According%20to%20the%202019%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20(NFHS-5)%2C%20Varanasi%20had%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20rates%20of%20Severe%20Acute%20Malnutrition%20(SAM)%20in%20the%20state.%20With%2013.3%20percent%20of%20its%20children%20aged%20zero%20to%20six%20classified%20as%20SAM%2C%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation%20demanded%20urgent%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERising%20to%20the%20challenge%2C%20the%20district%20magistrate%20S%20Rajalingam%20and%20chief%20development%20officer%20Himanshu%20Nagpal%20spearheaded%20a%20%E2%80%9810-Point%20Kashi%20Strategy%E2%80%99%20to%20tackle%20the%20crisis%20from%20multiple%20fronts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EVaranasi%E2%80%99s%2010-point%20strategy%3