%2C%20the%20malnourished%20children%20were%20given%20millet%20bars%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F306747%2Fkirti-yadav-kukclean-bengaluru-offers-plant-based-vegan-sugar-free-healthy-snacks-for-diabetes-patients%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eragi%20%3Cem%3Eladdoos%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20%3Cem%3EAnganwadis%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20improving%20attendance%20and%20retention.%20Earlier%2C%20only%20%3Cem%3Edaal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(pulses)%2C%20%3Cem%3Echana%3C%2Fem%3E%20(grams)%2C%20refined%20oil%2C%20and%20wheat%20were%20given%20to%20these%20families.%20Instead%2C%20we%20started%20distributing%20ready-to-eat%20items%20like%20%3Cem%3Ebarfi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(milk%20based%20sweet)%20and%20%3Cem%3Edaliya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(broken%20wheat)%20for%20the%20use%20of%20children.%20Almost%20one%20lakh%20SAM%20and%20MAM%20(moderate%20acute%20malnutrition)%20children%20are%20given%20these%20daily%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fvaranasi-malnutrition-4-1741180868.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Every%20day%2C%20the%20malnourished%20children%20are%20given%20millet%20bars%20and%20ragi%20laddoos%20at%20the%20anganwadis.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fvaranasi-malnutrition-4-1741180868.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fvaranasi-malnutrition-4-1741180868-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fvaranasi-malnutrition-4-1741180868-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fvaranasi-malnutrition-4-1741180868-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%