ent%2C%20further%20strengthening%20the%20programme%E2%80%99s%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBeyond%20books%3A%20Helping%20students%20find%20their%20voice%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20week%2C%20CybageKhushboo%E2%80%99s%20online%20classes%20focus%20on%20strengthening%20students%E2%80%99%20grammar%20skills.%20But%20Sundays%20bring%20a%20refreshing%20change%E2%80%94learning%20becomes%20interactive%2C%20engaging%2C%20and%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20students%20are%20divided%20into%20groups%20and%20given%20different%20topics%20to%20either%20enact%20as%20a%20play%20or%20discuss%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Prashant.%20%E2%80%9CPankaj%20conducts%20various%20activities%20that%20encourage%20active%20participation%20and%20build%20confidence.%20One%20key%20rule%20is%20that%20students%20must%20communicate%20exclusively%20in%20English%20during%20these%20sessions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20sharing%20personal%20experiences%20to%20reviewing%20books%20and%20movies%2C%20these%20discussions%20help%20students%20refine%20their%20communication%20skills%20in%20a%20supportive%20environment.%20By%20practising%20English%20in%20real-life%20scenarios%2C%20they%20gain%20the%20confidence%20to%20express%20themselves%20fluently%E2%80%94an%20invaluable%20skill%20that%20extends%20far%20beyond%20the%20classroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202908px)%20100vw%2C%202908px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FCK_4_11zon-1741342592.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222908%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20initiative%20helps%20almost%2095%25%20of%20its%20students%20land%20jobs%20in%20top%20companies%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FCK_4_11zon-1741342592.jpg%202908w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FCK_4_11zon-1741342592-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FCK_4_11zon-1741342592-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FCK_4_11zon-1741342592-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FCK_4_11zon-1741342592-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FCK_4_11zon-1741342592-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FCK_4_11zon-1741342592-1200x800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FCK_4_11zon-1741342592-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-412098%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221938%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20initiative%20helps%20almost%2095%25%20of%20its%20students%20land%20jobs%20in%20top%20companies%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFiza%2C%20another%20beneficiary%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20completed%20my%20school%20education%20at%20N.M.V%20Girls%20High%20School%2C%20and%20during%20my%20first%20year%20of%20college%20in%202019%2C%20I%20applied%20for%20a%20scholarship%20in%20July.%20By%20November%2C%20I%20received%20it%2C%20and%20that%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20my%20success.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Sunday%20classes%20helped%20me%20develop%20my%20soft%20skills.%20These%20sessions%20were%20incredibly%20valuable%2C%20teaching%20me%20how%20to%20navigate%20interviews%20and%20build%20my%20personality.%20Since%20I%20came%20from%20a%20Marathi%20medium%20background%2C%20English%20had%20always%20been%20a%20challenge%20for%20me.%20But%20through%20activities%20focused%20on%20personality%20building%2C%20communication%2C%20and%20English%20speaking%2C%20I%20slowly%20overcame%20my%20difficulties%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20soft%20skills%2C%20the%20initiative%20helped%20her%20learn%20coding%2C%20website%20development%2C%20and%20programming%20languages%20like%20C%2B%2B%20and%20Java%2C%20all%20of%20which%20supported%20her%20through%20her%20academic%20journey%20at%20MKSSS%E2%80%99s%20Cummins%20College%20of%20Engineering%2C%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20third%20year%2C%20when%20it%20was%20time%20for%20internships%2C%20I%20applied%20for%20an%20internship%20at%20Amazon.%20I%20attended%20the%20interview%2C%20and%20because%20of%20the%20confidence%20I%20gained%20through%20the%20sessions%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20perform%20well.%20I%20joined%20Amazon%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20intern%20for%20two%20months%2C%20and%20by%20the%20end%20of%20my%20internship%2C%20I%20received%20a%20pre-placement%20offer.%20In%202023%2C%20I%20officially%20joined%20Amazon%20with%20a%20CTC%20of%20around%2046%20LPA%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20Before%20joining%20Amazon%2C%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20mentor%2C%20taking%20technical%20sessions%20for%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20dreams%20into%20careers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20true%20impact%20of%20CybageKhushboo%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20success%20of%20its%20students.%20In%20the%20early%20years%2C%20only%2025%25%20of%20graduates%20were%20able%20to%20secure%20jobs%2C%20highlighting%20the%20challenges%20they%20faced%20beyond%20academics.%20Recognising%20this%2C%20the%20team%20expanded%20its%20focus%20in%202014%E2%80%94going%20beyond%20scholarships%20to%20equip%20students%20with%20essential%20soft%20skills%2C%20confidence-building%20exercises%2C%20and%20interview%20preparation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20have%20been%20remarkable.%20Today%2C%20an%20impressive%2095%25%20of%20students%20land%20jobs%20at%20leading%20companies%20through%20campus%20placements%2C%20proving%20that%20the%20right%20support%20can%20turn%20aspirations%20into%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20success%20story%20is%20that%20of%20Arjun%20Deshmukh%2C%20who%20secured%20a%20job%20at